evrouter (0.3.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added -q flag to kill the running daemon.
  * Fixed foreground mode that wouldn't. Many thanks to Stephen Graham for
    spotting this.
  * Updated manpage.
  * Spell-check manpage, spell-check manpage. Fix, fix.
  * Changed the configure.in package name from evwheel (the original
    project name) to evrouter. Again, thanks to Stephen Graham.
  * Removed bad-window message (unless --verbose was specified).
  * Added a newline to the bad-window message.

 -- Alexios Chouchoulas <alexios@bedroomlan.org>  Thu, 12 Feb 2004 00:32:54 +0000

